abstract: Egypt executes six men convicted of killing two military officers in skirmish at suspected bomb factory in Cairo in March 2014 and of belonging to ISIS affiliate Ansar Beit al-Maqdis; execution brings condemnation from Amnesty International.
lead_paragraph: Egypt executed six men Sunday who were convicted by a military court in connection with a gunfight last year at a suspected bomb factory.

headline.main: Egypt: 6 Executed in Killing of Police Officers
headline.print_headline: Middle East; Egypt: 6 Executed in Killing of Military Officers
